{"tid":2213667,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美科企對香港有信心  在港成立大中華總部","createTime":"2020-09-22T16:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T17:16:42.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"811cf089e3c28dc053801303b8692fca4c8928da","tid":2213667,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"疫情影響各行業發展，但不少科企卻一支獨秀，甚至「接單接到手軟」。來自美國、主力提供客戶體驗管理平台的Qualtrics，宣佈在港成立大中華總部，主力發展香港、台灣及澳門地區的業務。<br />\n<br />\n其大中華區總監 Pat Bolster將駐港，他接受訪問時表示，對香港金融中心地位有信心，計劃在港增聘員工，為客戶提供顧問及諮詢服務。「計劃至2021年，大中華總部人手增加至逾25人。」Pat指出，企業在發展及銷售過程中，除了要傳統的7Ps營銷理論，客戶的體驗愈趨重要，是吸引回頭客、品牌粉絲的重要因素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc85dffae6fb8f6034d90acfbdf07af66957be2","tid":2213667,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e409c6a29f1f7bd37ad28dc37052df171a53a75","tid":2213667,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:44:20.000Z","msg":"Silicon Valley要嚟次大掃除？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5083b06ba9873e3e9dea225abed639f82418e1b6","tid":2213667,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"總部得25條友 <br />\n保安隊黎"},{"pid":"7cc599a8d4fe92c2b0b6e01b635d63dfbb0dfdca","tid":2213667,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e409c6a29f1f7bd37ad28dc37052df171a53a75","tid":2213667,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:44:20.000Z","msg":"Silicon Valley要嚟次大掃除？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔駛<br />\n要入支那市場，除非你將成間公司拱手送比支那人<br />\n<br />\n否則你永遠唔會賺到錢"},{"